snippet: Though the national championship game was more challenging than the signal-caller thought, he joins quarterback royalty at F.S.U.
abstract: Jameis Winston joins quarterback royalty at Florida State University, by leading Seminoles to victory in the Bowl Championship Series national title game against Auburn; with 71 seconds left, Winston marched down the field, completing 6 of 7 passes for 77 yards, capping the drive by coolly lofting the winning 2-yard touchdown pass.
lead_paragraph: Though the national championship game was more challenging than the signal-caller thought, he joins quarterback royalty at F.S.U.

headline.main: Jameis Winston Smiles All the Way Into Seminole Lore
headline.print_headline: Winston Smiles All the Way Into Seminole Lore
